headline: CrowdStrike slumps more than 6% on weak earnings outlook, overhang from outage costs
text: CrowdStrike shares fell due to weak earnings guidance, impacted by July's global IT outage.

headline: Foot Locker results show the sneaker industry — and Nike — still have more pain ahead
text: Foot Locker expects continued deep discounts in the sneaker market due to Nike's inventory clearance efforts.

headline: MongoDB shares sink after company issues weak guidance
text: MongoDB shares plummeted 16% due to weak guidance despite exceeding Q4 earnings and revenue expectations.

headline: Broadcom shares soar 16% as earnings top estimates on demand for custom AI chips
text: Broadcom's strong earnings and guidance beat expectations, causing a 16% stock jump.

headline: Broadcom's report gives the battered AI trade a much-needed win
text: Broadcom shares surged after exceeding expectations with strong AI chip performance and optimistic guidance.

headline: Costco checks plenty of key boxes for investors despite missing on earnings
text: Costco's Q2 revenue beat expectations, showing continued growth driven by low prices amid economic uncertainty.

headline: Gap shares spike 17% as retailer blows away expectations again, showing turnaround has staying power
text: Gap's strong performance and successful turnaround, led by CEO Richard Dickson, caused a 17% stock jump.

headline: HPE to cut 2,500 employees as stock slides 19% on weak earnings outlook
text: HPE shares dropped 19% after disappointing guidance, as reported by CNBC from the NYSE floor.

headline: Macy's turnaround hinges on revamping some stores and closing others. It appears to be working
text: Macy's holiday sales fell; turnaround efforts and potential privatization create uncertainty for investors.

headline: Marvell plunges nearly 20% as outlook falls short of high expectations
text: Marvell stock dropped nearly 20% due to lower-than-expected revenue guidance, missing some investor targets.

headline: MongoDB plummets nearly 27% for worst day ever as weak outlook overshadows strong quarterly results
text: MongoDB's stock plummeted due to weak growth guidance for fiscal 2026, significantly missing analyst expectations.

headline: Broadcom shares rise as AI growth powers strong guidance
text: Broadcom's stock jumped 6% due to strong earnings and AI-driven demand outlook, surpassing analyst expectations.

headline: Volkswagen expects revenue to grow in 2025, says it feels 'all-American' as tariffs loom
text: Volkswagen's operating profit fell 15% due to rising costs and "extra strains," despite stock tracking promotion.

headline: American Eagle says consumer is slowing down, issues weak guidance
text: American Eagle reports a slower-than-expected start to 2025 due to weak demand and bad weather, anticipating spring improvements.

headline: Adobe shares drop 14% as concerns about AI growth overshadow better-than-expected results
text: Adobe CEO addressed B20 Summit; shares plummeted 14% after earnings due to AI monetization concerns.

headline: Dollar General store review and closures dent fourth-quarter earnings
text: Dollar General's Q4 revenue beat expectations, but profit suffered due to store closures and portfolio review.
